    <briefdescription>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>A circle-buffer-backed exponential counter.</para>
<para>The first recorded value becomes the &apos;base_index&apos;. Going backwards leads to start/stop index.</para>
<para>This expand start/end index as it sees values.</para>
<para>This class is NOT thread-safe. It is expected to be behind a synchronized incrementer. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
